| **P3 â€” Low** | 1.5, 1.6, 2.7, 3.2, 3.4, 3.5, 4.2, 4.3, 5.4, 5.5, 6.2, 6.3, 6.4, 6.5, 7.2, 7.4 | Nice-to-haves for production readiness |
